  <section class="grid_1_1">
    <div>
      <h2>History</h2>
      <p>
        2024 marks the 5th edition of Karrusel. Karrusel is a circus themed rave
        presenting some of the world's leading electronic artists.
      </p>
      <p>
        Past editions include performances by Acid Pauli, Amelie Lens, Dixon,
        FJAAK, Folamour, Hunee, Job Jobse, Kölsch, Mall Grab, Nastia,
        Partiboi69, Peggy Gou, Richie Hawtin, Skin On Skin, The Blessed Madonna,
        Victor Ruiz and VTSS.
      </p>
      <p>
        The festival is open air and takes place on secluded green spot at the
        abandoned shipyard of Refshaleøen in central Copenhagen.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>SUSTAINABILITY</h2>
      <p>
        Karrusel is committed to becoming more sustainable. In order to save
        resources and reduce waste we use left over materials and timber for
        stage designs and installations. We will re-use production and print
        materials when possible year after year. Beverages are served in
        reusable or sustainable materials. Straws are not being used.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>How you can help:</strong> Take a bike or public transport to the
        festival. Don’t bring confetti or glitter to the festival. There will be
        free tap water stations during the festival. Please bring an empty cup or
        bottle and drink nice free tap water.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="stjerne2_container">
