  <section>
    <h2>FESTIVAL EXPERIENCE</h2>
    <p>
      Karrusel believes in the right to a harassment-free festival experience.
      We believe in the right of everyone to express themselves.
    </p>
    <p>
      Karrusel welcomes everybody – all with their different orientations,
      experiences, histories and backgrounds. Karrusel only exists if everyone
      takes care of each other, respects their own and others boundaries,
      embraces diversity and acts as a part of the community.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you feel unsafe, please reach out to our awareness team. They will be
      wearing a pink vests and walk around the site and be at their base. Ask
      any festival staff and they will guide you to the them.
    </p>
    <p>
      Take responsibility for your own actions. Respect your own and others
      boundaries. Speak up rather than look the other way
    </p>
  </section>
